@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="card shadow rounded-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title mb-3">Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This Privacy Policy describes how Never Never Land (“NNL,” “we,” “our,” or “us”)
                        collects, uses, and safeguards your personal information when you visit our website,
                        create an account, or purchase tickets and passes. By using our site, you agree
                        to the practices described below.
                    </p>

                    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We may collect the following information:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Personal identifiers such as your name, email address, and phone number</li>
                            <li>Payment and billing details (processed securely through Stripe)</li>
                            <li>Account login details and purchase history</li>
                            <li>Technical data such as IP address, browser type, and usage activity</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>

                    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We use your information to:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Process ticket and pass purchases</li>
                            <li>Send confirmations, digital passes, and account notifications</li>
                            <li>Improve site performance and visitor experience</li>
                            <li>Ensure compliance with legal and security obligations</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>

                    <h4>3. Payment Processing</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Never Never Land does not store your credit card information. All payments are
                        processed through <strong>Stripe</strong>, a secure, PCI-compliant payment provider.
                        Please review Stripe’s Privacy Policy for details about their practices.
                    </p>

                    <h4>4. Email Communications</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We use <strong>SendGrid</strong> to deliver confirmation emails, digital passes,
                        and service notifications. You may opt out of promotional emails at any time,
                        but transactional messages (such as purchase confirmations) are required for service.
                    </p>

                    <h4>5. Data Security</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to
                        protect your personal information. While no system is completely secure,
                        we are committed to protecting your data from unauthorized access or misuse.
                    </p>

                    <h4>6. Sharing of Information</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We do not sell or rent your personal information. We only share data with trusted
                        third-party providers (e.g., Stripe, SendGrid) who assist in operating our services.
                        These providers are contractually obligated to protect your information.
                    </p>

                    <h4>7. Your Rights</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        You may request to access, update, or delete your personal information by
                        contacting us through your account or our support page. We will comply with
                        applicable data protection laws regarding your request.
                    </p>

                    <h4>8. Children’s Privacy</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Our website is not directed at anyone under the age of 18. We do not knowingly
                        collect information from children.
                    </p>

                    <h4>9. Policy Updates</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our
                        practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised
                        “Last Updated” date.
                    </p>

                    <p class="card-text mt-3">
                        <strong>Contact Us:</strong><br />
                        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br />
                        support@neverneverlandpark.com
                    </p>

                    <p class="card-text mt-3">
                        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> August 30, 2025
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
